# Metadata for SENSES.md

**Original location:** `More My Documents/wp/MONAS/SENSES`
**Date:** Undetermined
**Category:** research-notes aquinas bible hermeneutics

**Abstract:**
Notes on Aquinas's theory of senses of Scripture. Outlines literal/historical sense (first signification: words signify things) with subdivisions: historical, etiological, analogical, parabolical. Outlines spiritual/allegorical sense (second signification: things signified by words signify something else) with subdivisions: allegorical, moral, anagogical. Notes only literal sense can be source of argument, all other senses based on literal.

**AI Recommendation:** Keep in undated/notes - research notes for book project

